Package: il.cbs.muni
Title: Utility Functions to Work with Israeli Central Bureau of Statistics Municipal Data
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Matan", "Hakim", , "matanhakim@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-9372-8975"))
Description: Read and harmonize the municipal and locality data files published
  by the Israeli Central Bureau of Statistics (CBS). The published files change
  their layout, sheet order and identifier schemes from year to year, and these
  utilities work around those quirks to return tidy data with consistent
  identifiers. The package also harmonizes the several identifier systems used
  for Israeli local authorities and brings together data points from different
  years and sources, and it includes readers for the socio-economic and
  peripherality index publications.
